<div class='d-flex justify-content-end mb-3'>
  <%= link_to "https://occasion.cultura.com/", 
              target: "_blank", 
              rel: "noopener noreferrer", 
              class: 'c-btn align-right', 
              aria: { label: "Learn more on occasion.cultura.com" } do %>
    <span class="c-btn__label">Learn more on occasion.cultura.com →</span>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <%= image_tag 'cultura-main-photo.webp', 
                alt: "Cultura main appearance", 
                width: "1200", height: "675", 
                loading: "eager", class: "img-fluid" %>
</div>

<div class="row my-2 g-5">
  <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
    <%= image_tag 'cultura-1.webp', 
                  alt: "Cultura mobile view", 
                  width: "600", height: "800", 
                  loading: "lazy", class: "img-fluid" %>

    <div class="my-5 px-2">
      <h3>Challenges & Solutions</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Starting as an Entrepreneur</strong> – Led a project from the ground up, balancing technical and business aspects while delivering a quality product.</li>
        <li><strong>Building a Tablet-Only App</strong> – Designed and developed an app optimized for tablets, ensuring a smooth and responsive experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Using Bootstrap</strong> – Utilized Bootstrap for a responsive layout, making the app mobile-friendly and visually consistent.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5 px-2">
      <h3>Responsibilities</h3>
      <p><strong>Full-Stack Development</strong> – Contributed to front-end and back-end development in a Ruby on Rails web app.</p>
      <p><strong>UX & Graphic Design</strong> – Designed the UX and created graphic elements to align with the brand’s visual identity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
    <div class="mb-5 px-2">
      <h3>Overview</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Occasion by Cultura</strong> is a platform dedicated to offering second-hand items. The project aimed to develop a user-friendly web app for buying and selling pre-owned products, promoting sustainability and a seamless experience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <%= image_tag 'cultura-2.webp', 
                  alt: "Cultura shop tablet view", 
                  width: "800", height: "600", 
                  loading: "lazy", class: "img-fluid" %>

    <div class="p-3 row d-flex justify-content-start align-items-center my-5">
      <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4">
        <div class="horizontal-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-8 pt-3">
        <p>Visit the Cultura website to learn more about this project:</p>
        <%= link_to "https://occasion.cultura.com/", 
                    target: "_blank", 
                    rel: "noopener noreferrer", 
                    class: 'c-btn align-right', 
                    aria: { label: "Learn more on occasion.cultura.com" } do %>
          <span class="c-btn__label">Learn more on occasion.cultura.com →</span>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
